WE PROTECTED THE CITY.

257
00:22:51,125 --> 00:22:53,708
- YEAH.

258
00:23:01,000 --> 00:23:03,500
YOSHIDA.

259
00:23:06,958 --> 00:23:08,541
- YOU'RE ALIVE!

260
00:23:08,625 --> 00:23:11,250
- YEAH, I'M FINE.
